First record of the genus Arphthicarus Niedbała (Acari: Oribatida: Phthiracaridae) from China, with descriptions of two new speciesThe oribatid mite genus Arphthicarus Niedbała, 1994 (Phthiracaridae) is reported in China for the first time. Two new species of Arphthicarus are described: Arphthicarus baculus sp. nov. from Hunan Province, and Arphthicarus spiniformis sp. nov. from Guangxi Province.http://zoobank.org/urn:lsid:zoobank.org:pub:A1729EB7-2C99-4BF6-94EB-229E2A743D84.